                     <interp inst="t18200918-297-person2727" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was in the square with Wales, seized the prisoner, and took the pocket-book from his breeches,</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
